.SH NAME
_base_get_chain \- Calculates and Returns virtual chain address for the provided smid in BAR0 space.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void __iomem*" _base_get_chain
.BI "(struct MPT3SAS_ADAPTER *ioc "  ","
.BI "u16 smid "  ","
.BI "u8 sge_chain_count "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ioc" 12
per adapter object
.IP "smid" 12
system request message index
.IP "sge_chain_count" 12
Scatter gather chain count.
.SH "RETURN"
the chain address.
